Assignment 1: Basic Text Styling
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Text Styling</title>
    <style>
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            color: navy;
        }
        p {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: navy;
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Standard Typography Base</h1>
    <p>This paragraph uses clean Arial font configurations. The text alignment parameters distribute layout spacing uniformly across horizontal boundaries, ensuring tidy visual balance and clean layout structure alignment.</p>
</body>
</html>
