Assignment 3: Working with Borders and Shadows
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Borders and Shadows</title>
    <style>.profile-card {
            width: 300px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 2px solid #0066cc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            font-family: sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="profile-card">
        <h3>Design Profile Card</h3>
        <p>This card template features rounded corner configurations and soft box-shadow styling definitions to create clean depth.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
Assignment 4: Creating a Simple Navigation Bar
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Navigation Bar</title>
    <style>.navbar {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }.navbar a {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }.navbar a:hover {
            background-color: #555;
            color: #ffcc00;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">Services</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</body>
</html>
Assignment 5: Using Flexbox for Layout
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Flexbox Layout</title>
    <style>.app-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }
        header, footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        main {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
        }
        /* Media Query for larger screens */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            main {
                flex-direction: row;
                justify-content: space-around;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="app-container">
        <header><h1>Application Header</h1></header>
        <main>
            <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; margin: 10px; width: 200px;">Content Block 1</div>
            <div style="background: white; padding: 20px; margin: 10px; width: 200px;">Content Block 2</div>
        </main>
        <footer><p>Application Footer © 2026</p></footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
